arts.ttl: Kalimuendo has hat trick and Rennes thrashes Saint-Etienne in French league
arts.sum: Striker Arnaud Kalimuendo scored a hat trick and Rennes got back to winning ways in Ligue 1 by thrashing 10-man Saint-Etienne 5-0 on Saturday. Coach Jorge Sampaoli’s first win with his new team came in his second match in charge after he took over Rennes this month.
